# Fluxlive — Stream the Moment

Premium creator livestreaming for Africa and global youth culture.

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: Next.js + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Realtime)
- **Streaming**: LiveKit (coming soon)
- **Hosting**: Vercel (free)

## Features (MVP)

- ✅ User authentication (email signup/login)
- ✅ Dark neon UI with glassmorphism
- ✅ Landing page with Call-to-Action
- ✅ Database tables: users, streams, follows, messages, gifts, subscriptions

## Getting Started

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
